\c 52
\p
\v 1 Muka, muka, pfeka simba rako, iwe Ziyoni; pfeka nguvo dzako dzakaisvonaka, iwe Jerusarema, guta dzvene; nokuti kubva ikozvino hakungapinda mukati mako asina kudzingiswa neusina kunaka.
\v 2 Zvizunze kubva muguruva; simuka, ugare pasi, iwe Jerusarema; zvisunungure \add pa\add*zvisungo zvemutsipa wako, iwe mukunda wakatapwa weZiyoni.
\v 3 Nokuti anoreva seizvi Jehovha: Makazvitengeserwa pasina; zvino muchadzikunurwa pasina mari.
\v 4 Nokuti anoreva seizvi Ishe Jehovha: Vanhu vangu vakaburukira Egipita nguva yekare kunogarako sevatorwa, zvino muAsiriya wakavamanikidza pasina chikonzero.
\v 5 Zvino ikozvino ndinei pano, anoreva seizvi Jehovha, kuti vanhu vangu vanotorerwa pasina, vanotonga pamusoro pavo vanovaungudzisa, anoreva seizvi Jehovha, uye zita rangu rinoramba richinyombwa zuva rese.
\v 6 Naizvozvo vanhu vangu vachaziva zita rangu; naizvozvo nezuva iro \add vachaziva\add* kuti ndini ndinotaura; tarira, ndini.
\p
\v 7 Dzakanaka sei pamusoro pemakomo tsoka dzeanouya nemashoko akanaka, anoparidza rugare, anouya nemashoko akanaka ezvakanaka, anonzwisa ruponeso, anoti kuZiyoni: Mwari wako anotonga!
\v 8 Inzwi renharirire dzako! Vachasimudza inzwi, uye vachaimba zvikuru pamwe chete, nokuti vachaona ziso neziso, Jehovha paachadzosa Ziyoni.
\p
\v 9 Pururudzai nemufaro, imbai pamwe chete, imwi matongo eJerusarema, nokuti Jehovha wakanyaradza vanhu vake, wakadzikunura Jerusarema.
\v 10 Jehovha akafukura ruoko rwake rutsvene pameso pemarudzi ese; uye migumo yese yenyika ichaona ruponeso rwaMwari wedu.
\p
\v 11 Ibvai, ibvai, budai ipapo, musabata chinhu chine tsvina; budai pakati paro; ivai vakachena, imwi munotakura midziyo yaJehovha.
\v 12 Nokuti hamungabudi muchikurumidza, kana kuenda muchitiza; nokuti Jehovha achafamba pamberi penyu; Mwari waIsraeri achava muvhumbamiri mumashure.
\p
\v 13 Tarirai, muranda wangu achaita neuchenjeri, achakwiridzwa nekusimudzwa, nekukwirira kwazvo.
\v 14 Sezvo vazhinji vakashamiswa nemwi, kuonekwa kwaro kwakakuvara zvakadai, kupfuura upi neupi, nechimiro charo kupfuura vanakomana vevanhu.
\v 15 Saizvozvo achavhundusa marudzi mazhinji; madzimambo achapfumbira miromo yawo pamusoro pake, nokuti zvavasina kurondedzerwa vachazviona nezvavasina kunzwa vachazvinzwisisa.